cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.AR 

The paper proposes a model compression framework for efficient training and inference of deep neural networks on embedded systems. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories related to machine learning, computer vision, artificial intelligence, and neural networks. Specifically, cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), and cs.AR (Hardware Architecture) are all possible sub-categories that this paper could belong to.
